Pop. Milano Chairman May Leave Without Bonus, Corriere Reports

-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 
2011-10-11T06:16:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/pop-milano-chairman-may-leave-without-bonus-corriere-reports.html
Banca Popolare di Milano Scrl
Chairman Massimo Ponzellini is prepared to leave the bank
without a liquidation payment or bonus, daily Corriere della
Sera reported, citing an interview with the executive.  Ponzellini said he was “neutral” about his successor,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  